1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:32,632
=Episode 17=
(I love you. I love your perfections.)

3
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:40,270
(I love your flaws.
I love you simply because you are you.)

4
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:08,020
Xi, let's get married.

5
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:09,380
Okay.

6
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:05,500
The auspicious hour has arrived.

7
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:09,140
First, bow to Heaven.

8
00:02:10,260 --> 00:02:13,620
Thank Heaven for this blessed union.

9
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:19,420
Next, bow to Earth.

10
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:23,780
May the Earth bear witness
to your steadfast love.

11
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:29,500
Bow to one another.

12
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:36,700
Your hearts are joined in this life,
never to be changed.

13
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:41,739
Bind your hair as a pledge.

14
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:43,700
Perform the rite of joined hair.

15
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:45,899
From this day forth,
you are husband and wife.

16
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:48,060
May your love endure forever.

17
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:06,819
The ceremony is complete.

18
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:08,140
Now, to the bridal chamber.

19
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:18,379
What are you doing?

20
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:20,240
Aren't we going to liven up
the bridal chamber?

21
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,740
You're not yet of age.

22
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,699
There's so much for us to clean.

23
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,820
Let's go.

24
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:35,980
Zhao.

25
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:44,140
Why is your pulse in such disarray?

26
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:46,100
Your breath is really faint.

27
00:03:47,660 --> 00:03:49,380
What happened?

28
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:52,140
Now that we have completed the ceremony,

29
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,580
you ought to call me your husband.

30
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:59,420
You still have the mind to jest?

31
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:04,020
I have returned

32
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:07,420
my divine heart to Heavenly Dao.

33
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:15,660
Now,

34
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:17,860
I am nothing more

35
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,180
than a mortal through and through.

36
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:25,860
Don't leave me.

37
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:29,260
Zhao.

38
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,300
I love you.

39
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:39,980
I didn't hear you clearly.

40
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,700
Say it once more.

41
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:48,460
I said,

42
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,260
I love you.

43
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:53,700
I love you because you are you.

44
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:58,260
Whether you are a god or a mortal,

45
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:01,300
you are my most precious treasure.

46
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:03,980
It pains me to see you like this.

47
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,700
Don't cry.

48
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:14,580
Come now, no more tears.

49
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:19,580
With such beautiful eyes,

50
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,740
you should only shed tears of joy.

51
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:50,580
(If I tell Zhao
that I took out my demon heart,)

52
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:52,180
(he will surely be grieved.)

53
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,380
(I shall wait for another time)

54
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:56,940
(and find the right moment to tell him.)

55
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:30,259
Stop playing with it.

56
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,619
Get her lady here.

57
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:32,979
That seedling may be an illness.

58
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:34,500
Don't handle it carelessly.

59
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,500
You're making a fuss.

60
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:41,300
My lady.

61
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:44,059
A seedling is growing on my arm.

62
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:45,260
It's amusing.

63
00:06:50,740 --> 00:06:52,179
I think I've seen

64
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,940
this seedling somewhere before.

65
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:56,820
Zhao, do you recognize it?

66
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,379
I've never seen it.

67
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,380
Come here.

68
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:02,940
Do you feel any discomfort?

69
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:06,859
It feels like something
is spreading through my veins.

70
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:08,179
I have no strength.

71
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:10,380
It's growing from within your veins.

72
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,380
It itches.

73
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:18,300
Your senses are linked.

74
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:20,500
Bai, bear with it.

75
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:28,700
It hurts, my lady.

76
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:34,620
This strange plant
is bound to the flesh.

77
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:38,074
My lady, am I going to die?

78
00:07:38,075 --> 00:07:39,595
What are you saying?

79
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:41,300
I will not let you die.

80
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,179
- Bai!
- Bai.

81
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:46,820
Zhao, carry him to the side hall.

82
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,300
Lady He!

83
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:57,740
Lady He, everyone has
these strange plants on them.

84
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,179
They cannot be pulled out.

85
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,059
It hurts terribly.

86
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,059
Please, take a look.

87
00:08:01,060 --> 00:08:01,619
Lady He.

88
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:03,299
Please examine us, Lady He!

89
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,700
Lady He!

90
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,620
I don't want to die.

91
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:09,140
You cannot abandon us.

92
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:13,060
Lady He!

93
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:35,419
Lady He!

94
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:37,820
Honey, assist me.

95
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,260
Lady He.

96
00:09:08,380 --> 00:09:10,499
Lady He.

97
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,619
Help.

98
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:13,619
Chief Zhang also has
a strange plant growing on him.

99
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,899
He has gone mad.

100
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,820
He's trying to burn it off.

101
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:20,139
I'll go with you.

102
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:22,180
Why are these things growing on us?

103
00:09:24,260 --> 00:09:26,100
Zhao, listen to me.

104
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,580
From my assessment,

105
00:09:27,700 --> 00:09:30,099
this strange plant feeds on blood.

106
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:31,580
Its pollen spreads the infection.

107
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:34,139
The afflicted villagers
must not be allowed to leave.

108
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:34,979
Otherwise,

109
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:36,899
everyone in the village will perish.

110
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,979
Follow my instructions
and tend to the patients first.

111
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:40,220
I'll return shortly.

112
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:42,700
Be careful.

113
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:48,700
I don't want to become a monster.

114
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,740
Why has this happened to me?

115
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:53,580
Why? It's all because of this strange plant.

116
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,020
It hurts.

117
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:17,019
Chief Zhang, where are you?

118
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:17,739
Xi.

119
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:18,579
- Chief Zhang.
- Xi.

120
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:21,139
Xi, don't come any closer!
You need to leave!

121
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:23,499
I'll burn everything here down.

122
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:25,379
Otherwise, the entire village will die!

123
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,739
Chief Zhang, don't act rashly.

124
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:28,619
We can talk this through. Just come out.

125
00:10:28,620 --> 00:10:30,700
Go! Leave now!

126
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:36,020
Here.

127
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:39,580
There's a fire in the direction
of Chief Zhang's house.

128
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:40,940
What?

129
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:43,260
Chief Zhang's house

130
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:45,380
is full of fireworks powder.

131
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:52,700
Chief Zhang.

132
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,500
Xi.

133
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:54,980
Xi, don't come any closer!

134
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:02,940
Xi!

135
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:04,540
Xi!

136
00:11:10,620 --> 00:11:11,500
Xi!

137
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,860
Do you hear me?

138
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,180
Xi!

139
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:16,860
Xi!

140
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:24,659
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

141
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:27,509
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

142
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:30,249
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

143
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:31,879
♪Let the long shadows♪

144
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:37,480
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

145
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:39,129
♪If in a dream♪

146
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:41,889
♪I can hear your voice♪

147
00:11:41,890 --> 00:11:44,739
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

148
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:47,339
♪Let it be us♪

149
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:52,129
♪drawing endlessly close♪

150
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:53,889
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

151
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:56,540
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

152
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:59,479
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

153
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,129
♪Not even in time♪

154
00:12:01,130 --> 00:12:06,789
♪to tell you how I feel♪

155
00:12:06,790 --> 00:12:08,329
♪If the rain won't stop♪

156
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:11,079
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

157
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:14,049
♪Let love go on♪

158
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:16,599
♪Until forever♪

159
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:21,239
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

160
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:23,849
♪Until forever♪

161
00:12:23,850 --> 00:12:30,960
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
